---
import MainLayout from "@/layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<MainLayout title="About Us">
  <section class="py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <!-- Hero Section -->
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Our Story</h1>
        <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-primary mx-auto mb-8"></div>
        <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Discover the passion and craftsmanship behind our exclusive perfume
          collection. Every scent tells a story, and every bottle captures a
          moment.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Our Journey -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-24">
        <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1608528577891-eb055944f2e7"
            alt="Perfume artisan at work"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Our Journey</h2>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">
            Founded in 2010 in the heart of Grasse, France - the world's perfume
            capital - our perfume house began as a small artisanal workshop with
            just three passionate perfumers. We were dedicated to creating
            unique, handcrafted fragrances that stand apart from mass-produced
            scents, using only the finest natural ingredients sourced from
            sustainable farms around the world.
          </p>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">
            Our founder, Master Perfumer Jean-Luc Moreau, brought over 20 years
            of experience from prestigious perfume houses before establishing
            our brand. He set out to create fragrances that tell stories and
            evoke emotions, drawing inspiration from his travels across six
            continents and his deep knowledge of traditional perfume-making
            techniques.
          </p>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">
            In our first five years, we gained recognition by winning three
            international fragrance awards, including the prestigious Prix
            International du Parfum in 2014. This helped us expand from our
            original 500 sq ft workshop to a state-of-the-art facility while
            maintaining our small-batch production philosophy.
          </p>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">
            Today, we're proud to have grown into one of the most respected
            names in artisanal perfumery, with our creations being featured in
            luxury boutiques across 32 countries. Despite this growth, we remain
            committed to our core values of quality, creativity, and sustainable
            practices - each bottle is still hand-filled and inspected by our
            team of expert perfumers.
          </p>
          <div class="pt-4">
            <a
              href="/products"
              class="px-6 py-3 bg-black text-white rounded-md hover:bg-black/90 transition-colors font-medium inline-flex items-center gap-2"
            >
              <i class="fas fa-flask"></i>
              Explore Our Collection
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Our Philosophy -->
      <div
        class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 to-primary/10 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 mb-24 mx-auto w-full max-w-screen-2xl px-8"
      >
        <div class="text-center max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Our Philosophy</h2>
          <p class="text-lg mb-8">
            We believe that perfume is more than just a fragranceâ€”it's an
            expression of individuality, a trigger for memories, and a
            complement to life's special moments.
          </p>
          <div
            class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-4 px-2"
          >
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-md">
              <div
                class="w-14 h-14 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3"
              >
                <i class="fas fa-leaf text-xl text-primary"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Sustainability</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
                Using ethically sourced ingredients and eco-friendly packaging
                to minimize our environmental impact.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-md">
              <div
                class="w-14 h-14 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3"
              >
                <i class="fas fa-flask text-xl text-primary"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Craftsmanship</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
                Blending traditional techniques with modern innovation to create
                complex, sophisticated fragrances.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-md">
              <div
                class="w-14 h-14 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3"
              >
                <i class="fas fa-heart text-xl text-primary"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Inclusivity</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
                Creating scents that transcend gender, age, and cultural
                boundaries, making perfume accessible to all.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-md">
              <div
                class="w-14 h-14 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3"
              >
                <i class="fas fa-seedling text-xl text-primary"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Natural Ingredients</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
                Prioritizing pure, natural essences that are gentle on skin and
                the environment.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-md">
              <div
                class="w-14 h-14 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3"
              >
                <i class="fas fa-star text-xl text-primary"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Luxury Experience</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
                Every bottle delivers an elevated sensory experience, from
                fragrance to packaging.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Our Process -->
      <div class="mb-24">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">
          Our Perfume Creation Process
        </h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div
              class="w-20 h-20 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 relative"
            >
              <span
                class="absolute -top-3 -right-3 w-8 h-8 bg-black text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold"
                >1</span
              >
              <i class="fas fa-lightbulb text-2xl text-primary"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Inspiration</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground">
              Each scent begins with a concept, a story we want to tell through
              fragrance.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div
              class="w-20 h-20 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 relative"
            >
              <span
                class="absolute -top-3 -right-3 w-8 h-8 bg-black text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold"
                >2</span
              >
              <i class="fas fa-search text-2xl text-primary"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Ingredient Selection</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground">
              We source the finest raw materials from around the world, focusing
              on quality and sustainability.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div
              class="w-20 h-20 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 relative"
            >
              <span
                class="absolute -top-3 -right-3 w-8 h-8 bg-black text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold"
                >3</span
              >
              <i class="fas fa-vial text-2xl text-primary"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Composition</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground">
              Our master perfumers craft the formula, balancing notes to create
              a harmonious and complex scent.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div
              class="w-20 h-20 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 relative"
            >
              <span
                class="absolute -top-3 -right-3 w-8 h-8 bg-black text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold"
                >4</span
              >
              <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-2xl text-primary"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Refinement</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground">
              Each fragrance undergoes extensive testing and refinement until it
              achieves perfection.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonials -->
      <div
        class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 to-primary/10 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 mb-24"
      >
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">
          What Our Customers Say
        </h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md relative">
            <div class="absolute -top-5 left-6">
              <i class="fas fa-quote-left text-4xl text-primary/20"></i>
            </div>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-6 pt-4">
              "I've tried many perfumes over the years, but nothing compares to
              the depth and longevity of these fragrances. My signature scent
              never fails to get compliments."
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full overflow-hidden mr-4">
                <img
                  src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/32.jpg"
                  alt="Customer"
                  class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                />
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold">Jessica M.</h4>
                <div class="flex text-yellow-400">
                  <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                  <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                  <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                  <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                  <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md relative">
            <div class="absolute -top-5 left-6">
              <i class="fas fa-quote-left text-4xl text-primary/20"></i>
            </div>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-6 pt-4">
              "The attention to detail in these perfumes is remarkable. I
              appreciate how each scent evolves throughout the day, revealing
              different notes as time passes."
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full overflow-hidden mr-4">
                <img
                  src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/46.jpg"
                  alt="Customer"
                  class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                />
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold">Robert T.</h4>
                <div class="flex text-yellow-400">
                  <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                  <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                  <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                  <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                  <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md relative">
            <div class="absolute -top-5 left-6">
              <i class="fas fa-quote-left text-4xl text-primary/20"></i>
            </div>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-6 pt-4">
              "I love supporting a brand that prioritizes sustainability. The
              fact that these perfumes are both eco-friendly and luxurious makes
              them the perfect choice."
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full overflow-hidden mr-4">
                <img
                  src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/65.jpg"
                  alt="Customer"
                  class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                />
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold">Aisha K.</h4>
                <div class="flex text-yellow-400">
                  <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                  <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                  <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                  <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                  <i class="fas fa-star-half-alt"></i>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA Section -->
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Experience Our Collection</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground mb-8">
          Ready to discover your signature scent? Explore our collection of
          handcrafted perfumes and find the fragrance that speaks to you.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
          <a
            href="/products"
            class="px-8 py-4 bg-black text-white rounded-md hover:bg-black/90 transition-colors font-medium shadow-md inline-flex items-center gap-2"
          >
            <i class="fas fa-shopping-bag"></i>
            Shop Now
          </a>
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="px-8 py-4 border border-black text-black rounded-md hover:bg-black/5 transition-colors font-medium inline-flex items-center gap-2"
          >
            <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
            Contact Us
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
